{"tid":31030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有咩好狂賀 只係換另一個傀儡","createTime":"2016-12-09T12:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T12:37:27.000Z","uid":32403,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a087fa92d4029acc35d5198f99a046442c3f21ca","tid":31030,"uid":32403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"見到好多人慶祝689終於收皮<br />\n個人黎講 佢的確值得收皮 應有此報<br />\n不過又有咩咁需要狂賀呢<br />\n<br />\n難道有人會認為下一屆特首比前三屆都好？<br />\n不了 肯定只係共匪第四個傀儡特首<br />\n而且肯定越來越聽話 係聽共匪話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43d6c59377a8e4f71ebbf1eef39b56a179ca811","tid":31030,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"所以我都唔明有乜咁開心<br />\n一陣換個毒瘤上去硬推23條立法<br />\n到時咪仲衰嘅狼震鷹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288cfcafe395b9b51c07fe98497c5a3d6ddec73b","tid":31030,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"冇分別既即係你支持689連任？"},{"pid":"79e331aae71f874cae2678f28f80675ff571122f","tid":31030,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"做得唔好就要換<br />\n未上台嗰啲上左台再屌"},{"pid":"5d1487d86dce238ea080fa54e10792aa29359b2e","tid":31030,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇分別既即係你支持689連任？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人立場就無話支唔支持<br />\n依家只不過係舊傀儡爛左換個舊新嘅上去<br />\n特首邊個做 我地有得話事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地連選擇權都無 可以做得嘅乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf6e12eec7329368bac8c468775a5281fd4e5a9","tid":31030,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"港豬係天真架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif